<node TEXT="changes committed" ID="ID_1011616177" CREATED="1357173515040" MODIFIED="1357177242085">
<node TEXT="(1) Add last step to makefile that merges the three outputs into a single monolithic file. (2) Infer client and plan_code from patient data rather than claims data. Doing that involved (a) changing patient-month-client-plan aggregates (of claims) to patient-month aggregates; (b) dropping client and plan_code from the claims data; (c) moving the creation of the single variable encoding client and plan from the pm claims file to the monolith pm file. (3) Delete hangovers: Drop patient-months generated by the distribution of claims across future months when that future is a period of non-enrollment. (Example: If someone got a 3-month prescription in Dec 2008 and was not enrolled in 2009, drop Jan and Feb 2009.)" ID="ID_1213192433" CREATED="1357173525423" MODIFIED="1357177193766"/>
</node>
</node>
