<node TEXT="    &#x201c;The research or demonstration project is to be conducted by or subject to the approval of state or local government officials and is designed to study, evaluate, or otherwise examine: (i) public benefit or service programs; (ii) procedures for obtaining benefits or services under those programs; (iii) possible changes in or alternatives to those programs or procedures; (iv) possible changes in methods or levels of payments for benefits or services under those programs, and&#xa;    The research could not practicably be carried out without the waiver or alteration.&#x201d;" ID="ID_701731512" CREATED="1370305984748" MODIFIED="1370305985690"/>
